title: Mr. Trendsident 1/8: The Weeknd, Daddy Hat Girl, ID, Tommy Lasorda, Joe Manchin

description:
On this edition of Mr. Trendsident Jack and Miles discuss The Weeknd taking off his bandages, Daddy Hat Girl's interview with Gayle King, the internet has gone to work identifying the terrorists who invaded the Capitol, former Dodger's Manager Tommy Lasorda has passed, and Joe Manchin is AGAINST $2000 checks.
